	author = {Dinnes, Jacqueline and Deeks, Jonathan J and Berhane, Sarah and Taylor, Melissa and Adriano, Ada and Davenport, Clare and Dittrich, Sabine and Emperador, Devy and Takwoingi, Yemisi and Cunningham, Jane and Beese, Sophie and Domen, Julie and Dretzke, Janine and Ferrante di Ruffano, Lavinia and Harris, Isobel M and Price, Malcolm J and Taylor-Phillips, Sian and Hooft, Lotty and Leeflang, Mariska MG and McInnes, Matthew DF and Spijker, René and Van den Bruel, Ann and Arevalo-Rodriguez, I. and Buitrago, D.C. and Ciapponi, A. and Mateos, M. and Stuyf, T. and Horn, S. and Salameh, J.P. and McGrath, T.A. and van der Pol, C.B. and Frank, R.A. and Prager, R. and Hare, S.S. and Dennie, C. and Jenniskens, K. and Korevaar, D.A. and Cohen, J.F. and van de Wijgert, J. and Damen, J.A.A.G. and Wang, J. and Agarwal, R. and Baldwin, S. and Herd, C. and Kristunas, C. and Quinn, L. and Scholefield, B.},
