eas the qualitative was based on rubrics. The findings revealed that there is significant improvement not only in the writing skills of experimental group students but also listening, speaking, and reading skills, leading to effective communication skills in English Language. © 2023, Rajarambapu Institute Of Technology. All rights reserved.},
